Package: fspp
Title: Fourier Analysis for Spatial Point Processes
Version: 0.1.0.0000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Qi-Wen", "Ding", email = "r07227101@ntu.edu.tw", role = c("aut")),
    person("Junho", "Yang", email = "junhoyang@stat.sinica.edu.tw", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Frequency domain method for multivariate (multitype) inhomogeneous
    spatial point processes on rectangle region. Given a multivariate point pattern
    and parametric model of the intensity function, this package provides the kernel
    spectral estimate of the pseudo-spectrum, the frequency-domain representation of
    inhomogeneous point process. Functions for bandwidth selection, visualization, 
    and coherence analysis for inhomogeneous point processes are also provided.
